cs.LG, cs.CV, cs.AI, cs.NE, cs.DS

The paper discusses transfer learning for deep neural networks in the context of time series classification. Therefore, the most likely sub-category is cs.LG (Machine Learning), followed by cs.CV (Computer Vision) as transfer learning has been extensively studied in this field. The paper also involves the use of deep neural networks, which suggests cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence) and cs.NE (Neural and Evolutionary Computing) as possible sub-categories. Finally, the paper deals with time series data, which could also place it in the cs.DS (Data Structures and Algorithms) sub-category.
